        <div1 type="body">
            


<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName> Dr
To <persName>Francis Major</persName></p>

<p>For the hire of <persName>Toney </persName>from the <date when="1811-01-14">14 of Jany 1811</date>
To the 16th of March following at $18,00 per Month</p>

<p>is_______________________________________	 $37. 50

<date when="1811-04-02">2nd April</date> 1 Days Work____________________    0. 75
							 _______
							 $38. 25
							 _______
<persName>Mr. Austin</persName> dtr___________________________  $36. 00

Crdt_____________________________________   $3. 62 1/2

Balance Due______________________________  $32. 37 1/2</p>

<p><placeName>Mine a Burton</placeName>
	<date when="1811-04-24">April 24 1811</date>   Recd. <persName>M Austin</persName> Note for the above <persName>Negro </persName>Hire
which when paid is in full of all accounts                   <persName>Fras. Major</persName></p>


        </div1>
